<subSubSection id="C317ABC4D9617A31FF2CFF1AFD28DF5A" pageId="16" pageNumber="539" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BB2F84FD9617A31FF2CFF1AFD28DF5A" blockId="16.[151,1436,153,323]" pageId="16" pageNumber="539">
<emphasis id="B979245DD9617A31FF2CFF1AFED9DEE2" bold="true" box="[199,322,224,251]" pageId="16" pageNumber="539">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Prothorax with laterocentral tubercle, the sides straight anteriorly and posteriorly; elytra with centrobasal crest without setae on top, with median dorsal carina, ornate with granules bearing setae, without lateral carina. Number of species currently included: 2.
</paragraph>
